modName: Dark Brotherhood servants of the mother
summary: This mod adds 4 new members to the the dark brotherhood in dawnstar, one of them being a pet talking dog. Important!!!: you have to have finished the dark brothehood qeust, otherwise there wil be problems with the sanctuary! enjoy it :)
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds 4 new members to the the dark brotherhood in dawnstar, one of them being a pet talking dog. Important!!!: you have to have finished the dark brothehood qeust, otherwise there wil be problems with the sanctuary! 
Adds:
Brutus the talking pet dog
Ralfina the dark elf mage (folower)
Zenor the torturer
Also adds Veezara back to the dark brothehood faction(folower)
author: Pietpompies
